Our operations continue to be disrupted by local denizens. Put a stop to it.

Kill the {@LinkCreature:55#4#feystalker sabertooths}, {@LinkCreature:55#3#Bloodgulper orcans}, and {@LinkCreature:55#2#unstable mycanars}.

Report to Laena at Ceravin Point when mission is complete.
You've earned the thanks of the federation!
It looks like you haven't completed your mission yet.
